  <summary date="2021-10-26T17:10:08Z" status="Introduced in House">Second Chance Opportunity for Re-Entry Education Act of 2021 or the SCORE Act of 2021

This bill directs the Bureau of Justice Assistance within the Department of Justice to establish a grant program&#8212;the Second Chance Opportunity for Re-Entry Education Grant Program&#8212;to promote reentry training programs and reduce recidivism to county jails for qualified nonviolent inmates.</summary>
